pageContent: Purpose: To describe outcomes of men with unfavorable (high-tier) intermediate risk prostate cancer (H-IR) treated with low-dose-rate (LDR) brachytherapy, with or without 6 months of androgen deprivation therapy (ADT).

metaData.source:
Development of South Australian-Victorian Prostate Cancer Health Outcomes Research Dataset
